In the room, a qingyi youth, some leng God looked at a transparent jade put in front. Exactly, the boy is not looking at the jade, but at the liquid inside the jade. At this point, a pungent white smoke, is slowly spreading from the liquid.



The boy was named 6 Chen, a legitimate son of 6 families.
